Melbourne’s coffee business growth: Age and Income Are Not Key Factors

Author

Phuong Anh Le

Published

October 6, 2024

Welcome to the cafeMel Shiny app!

Melbourne has been renowned for its vibrant coffee culture, often celebrated as the coffee capital of Australia. From cozy laneway cafes to lively coffee roasteries, the city’s coffee scene has experienced remarkable growth over the past few decades. But what drives this surge in coffee shops across Melbourne? This app provides an interactive exploration of coffee shop distribution among Melbourne’s suburbs, examining how factors such as residents’ age and income levels might influence these trends. Dive in to uncover insights about the dynamics behind Melbourne’s coffee culture!
